OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FBy ITV News Multimedia Producer Connor
OL,7,FParker
OL,9,FThe United States and Iran have
OL,10,Freached an interim deal aimed at
OL,11,Fending the war and reopening the
OL,12,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,14,FThe deal was signed by US President
OL,15,FDonald Trump and Iranian President
OL,16,FMasoud Pezeshkian on Wednesday
OL,17,Fevening, with Trump signing a paper
OL,18,Fcopy of the Memorandum of
OL,19,FUnderstanding at the Palace of
OL,20,FVersailles while he was attending the
OL,21,FG7 summit in Paris.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
