OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781779675
OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FIt calls for Tehran to dilute its
OL,7,Fstockpile of highly enriched uranium
OL,8,Fand waives several US-backed sanctions
OL,9,Fon the country, immediately allowing
OL,10,FIran to sell its oil freely.
OL,12,FIt also opens the Strait of Hormuz
OL,13,Fwithout tolls for two months, but does
OL,14,Fnot preclude fees in the future,
OL,15,Faccording to details shared by both
OL,16,Fsides.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781779675
OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FBut while some of the main commitments
OL,7,Fare known, the exact details of the
OL,8,Fagreement have not yet been published
OL,9,F- and numerous thorny issues have been
OL,10,Fleft unresolved.
OL,12,FThis means nobody knows if the deal
OL,13,Fwill last.
OL,15,FIt is quickly becoming controversial
OL,16,Fin the US, with some of Trump's
OL,17,FRepublican Party already criticising
OL,18,Fit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
