OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781779675
OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Israel has also said it
OL,7,Fwill not withdraw from land seized in
OL,8,FLebanon and plans to continue its
OL,9,Fcampaign against Hezbollah.
OL,11,FThis is despite Iran tying the interim
OL,12,Fdeal to halting Israel's attacks on
OL,13,FHezbollah in Lebanon.
OL,15,FBoth the US and Israel launched the
OL,16,Fwar on February 28, striking numerous
OL,17,Ftargets in Iran, with Iran responding
OL,18,Fby blocking the Strait and attacking
OL,19,FUS allies in the region. Israel
OL,20,Finvaded Lebanon weeks later.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
