OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FA ceasefire was agreed on April 8, but
OL,7,Ftensions remained high with the US
OL,8,Fblockading Iran's ports and Iran
OL,9,Frefusing to open the Strait.
OL,11,FNations across the world have been
OL,12,Feager for the conflict to end amid
OL,13,Ffears of the impact on the global
OL,14,Feconomy.
OL,16,FWorld leaders and international
OL,17,Fmarkets have welcomed the agreement,
OL,18,Fwith all sides keen to see the Strait
OL,19,Fof Hormuz reopened. There is a huge
OL,20,Fincentive to make the deal a permanent
OL,21,Fpeace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
