OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FHere is what to know about it.
OL,8,FA 60-day period to attempt to address
OL,9,FIran's nuclear programme
OL,11,FThe US and Israel fear Iran's nuclear
OL,12,Fprogramme could lead to an atomic
OL,13,Fweapon, and it was a main reason their
OL,14,Fleaders cited for going to war.
OL,16,FTehran has insisted its nuclear
OL,17,Fprogramme is peaceful, though it has
OL,18,Fenough highly enriched uranium to
OL,19,Fbuild several atomic bombs, should it
OL,20,Fchoose to do so.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
