PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781779675
OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FThe agreement signed on Wednesday
OL,7,Fnight calls for the International
OL,8,FAtomic Energy Agency (IAEA) to monitor
OL,9,Fthe "downblending" of Iran's uranium,
OL,10,Fwithout elaborating on what that means
OL,11,Fexactly.
OL,13,FA senior US administration official
OL,14,Ftold the Associated Press on Friday
OL,15,Fthat the emerging agreement would
OL,16,Fbegin the process of destroying or
OL,17,Fremoving Tehran's highly enriched
OL,18,Furanium.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
