OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FThat's something disputed by Iran,
OL,7,Fwhich has insisted it would hold onto
OL,8,Fits stockpile.
OL,10,FThe official said the 60 days would be
OL,11,Fused to work out technical details for
OL,12,Fremoving the uranium.
OL,14,FThe official did not say who the US
OL,15,Fenvisions taking charge of removing
OL,16,Fthe uranium, which is believed to be
OL,17,Fentombed under three nuclear sites
OL,18,Fbattered by US strikes last year.
OL,20,FRussia has also offered to take the
OL,21,Fmaterial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
