OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FThe Strait of Hormuz will be reopened
OL,8,FThe US official the Associated Press
OL,9,Fspoke to said the emerging agreement
OL,10,Fincludes provisions for reopening the
OL,11,Fstrait, a crucial waterway for global
OL,12,Foil and gas transport.
OL,14,FIran Foreign Minister Abbas Araghchi
OL,15,Fsaid the country wants a deal that
OL,16,Fallows Tehran to charge ships "for
OL,17,Fservices rendered" when they transit
OL,18,Fthe Strait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
