OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781779675
OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FIran started charging vessels for
OL,7,Fpassage during the war, which the US
OL,8,Fand other nations have said violates
OL,9,Finternational law.
OL,11,FIran has also said it will only reopen
OL,12,Fthe Strait if the US ends the blockade
OL,13,Fof its ports.
OL,15,FThe Strait has long been considered
OL,16,Finternational waters, though it lies
OL,17,Fwithin the territorial waters of Iran
OL,18,Fand Oman.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
