OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FTransit through the Strait has
OL,7,Fdisrupted global energy supplies,
OL,8,Fdriven up fuel prices, and made food
OL,9,Fand other basics like fertiliser more
OL,10,Fexpensive well beyond the region.
OL,12,FWhen US President Donald Trump
OL,13,Fannounced the deal on Sunday, he said:
OL,14,F"I hereby fully authorise the toll
OL,15,Ffree opening of the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,16,Fand, simultaneously herewith,
OL,17,Fauthorise the immediate removal of the
OL,18,FUnited States Naval blockade. Ships of
OL,19,Fthe World, start your engines. Let the
OL,20,Foil flow!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
