OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FWhat will happen to Lebanon remains
OL,7,Funclear
OL,9,FThe prime minister of Pakistan, who
OL,10,Fhas been acting as a mediator, said
OL,11,Fafter the deal had been announced that
OL,12,F"both sides have declared the
OL,13,Fimmediate and permanent termination of
OL,14,Fmilitary operations on all fronts,
OL,15,Fincluding in Lebanon".
OL,17,FBut Israel has seemingly rejected that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
