OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FDefence Minister Israel Katz said the
OL,7,Fcountry will not withdraw from land
OL,8,Fseized in Lebanon as the interim deal
OL,9,Fis pending.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FKatz said Israel plans to stay
OL,17,F"indefinitely" in lands it holds in
OL,18,FLebanon, as well as Syria and the Gaza
OL,19,FStrip.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
