OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FKatz also threatened that if Iran
OL,7,Fattacks Israel, Israel will strike
OL,8,FIran with "great force".
OL,10,FDespite a ceasefire between Lebanon
OL,11,Fand Israel being in place, Israel and
OL,12,FHezbollah, which is based in Lebanon,
OL,13,Fhave been fighting nearly continuously
OL,14,Ffor months.
OL,16,FOn Sunday, hours before the US and
OL,17,FIran agreed on the deal, Israel
OL,18,Flaunched strikes on Beirut targeting
OL,19,FHezbollah.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
