OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FTrump criticised this after both the
OL,7,FUS and Iran warned against attacking
OL,8,FBeirut directly while the peace talks
OL,9,Fwere ongoing.
OL,11,FHezbollah has repeatedly said it does
OL,12,Fnot recognise deals signed by Lebanon
OL,13,Fand has vowed to continue fighting
OL,14,Fwith Israel as long as they maintain a
OL,15,Fpresence in Lebanon.
OL,17,FThe US could pay Iran a lot of money
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
