OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781779675
OL,3,CIs the war over? Everything to know
OL,4,Cabout the latest US-Iran deal
OL,6,FThree regional officials said the
OL,7,Femerging deal was expected to include
OL,8,Fthe phased lifting of sanctions on
OL,9,FIran and the release of frozen Iranian
OL,10,Fassets, which amount to tens of
OL,11,Fbillions of dollars.
OL,13,FIt has also been reported that Trump
OL,14,Fis considering paying for some of
OL,15,FIran's reconstruction costs if they
OL,16,Fcooperate in removing nuclear material.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/16
